    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、こころちゃんの実家に無事に到着しました～！\nこころちゃんのお母さんも、初めまして～！",
      "startTime": 6.8666666388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "同じ事務所の、kanaで～す\n今日はお邪魔させてもらって、ありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 12.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "ここが、こころちゃんちのリビングですが……広～い！\nソファもオシャレだし、なんか家具屋さんみたい！",
      "startTime": 22.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、こころちゃんがそこでふんぞり返ってる！\n高そうなソファなんだから、もう少し大事に座ろうよ",
      "startTime": 30.6024611369,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4649.8068635,
          "startTime": 35.2522680004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "だって、こころが子供の時からあるソファだし\n事務所の寮に入る前は、いっつもお昼寝してたし",
      "startTime": 39.5999999721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "えー、こっちの窓も、都内が一望出来て凄いんですけど\nプライバシー保護のため、モザイクでお送りします",
      "startTime": 49.2999999721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "視聴者のみなさんは、各自タワマンの眺めを想像して\nここら辺に、はめ込んどいて下さ～い！",
      "startTime": 57.0666666388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "窓の外なんて、あんま変わらないと思うんですけどねー\nねえ、お母さん、冷蔵庫にジュースあるー？",
      "startTime": 65.6333333055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、カトリーヌ！　こころだよ、ただいま～！！",
      "startTime": 69.1206575435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　カトリーヌって誰のこと……\n……うわ～、猫ちゃんだ～！　可愛い～～！！",
      "startTime": 78.5333333055,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3022.6761140999943,
          "startTime": 77.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "毛がふかふかー、ぬいぐるみみたーい！\nねえ、kanaも撫でていい……あっ、行っちゃった",
      "startTime": 86.2999999721,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5086.009438499999,
          "startTime": 87.5999999721
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "カトちゃんはこころも滅多に撫でさせてもらえない\n我が家のお嬢様なのです",
      "startTime": 95.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、こころちゃんもお嬢様でしょ。こんな\nドラマのセットみたいな家、kana、初めて来たよ",
      "startTime": 101.6666666388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、お嬢様だなんて\nそんなことは…………ちょっとはありますけど～？",
      "startTime": 108.3333333055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "あははは、こころちゃん、正直過ぎ！！",
      "startTime": 113.3079348606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.0999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_chime-07.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "実家レポは、これだけ撮っとけば十分ですよね\n後はスタッフさんが、編集でなんとかしてくれますよ",
      "startTime": 122.6999999721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "そうねー。…………それはそうと、あんた\n実家のことテレビで公開しちゃって、良かったの？",
      "startTime": 131.4999999721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "小学校で最初にイジメられた原因って、確か\n「どうせ親が金持ちだから」って言われたせいでしょ",
      "startTime": 138.8666666388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "やだな～、そんな話まで覚えてたんですか\n昔のことですし、もう全然気にしてませんってば",
      "startTime": 146.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに中学生にもなってそんなこと言う人いませんし\nあ、でもお嬢様キャラにチェンジはちょっと嫌ですねぇ",
      "startTime": 155.7741491361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "だって星見プロには、もう、すずにゃんがいますから\n二番煎じだと思われたら、少し悔しいじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 164.9666666388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、お母さんが呼んでるんで、行ってきますね！",
      "startTime": 169.3141717318,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2719.161601499991,
          "startTime": 172.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "……あいつ、演技の仕事は当分無理だな\n目が泳いでるの、全然誤魔化せてないじゃん",
      "startTime": 177.7666615526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_02-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "……ったく\n意地を張るなら、もうちょっとうまくやれっての",
      "startTime": 182.9666605353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
